Name: Dream Girls Collection
About the game: Hello! We want to meet you! There are different animal girls among us, we live in different biomes, and we have different habits and characters. Someone is gentle, and it is better not to get close to someone. Who do you like the most? CHARACTERS Milk girl Height: 166 cm Three sizes: B97 / W58 / H93 Birthday July 5 Herbivorous Habitat - Fields Favorite food - Grass, oats. TEMPER Hi! I'm a very gentle girl, really, really! I really like to lie in the sun on the juicy grass and soak… Juicy grass by the way, this is my weakness… And in the morning, you will always have a glass of warm milk! Tropical girl Height: 166 cm Three sizes: B97 / W58 / H93 Birthday December 11 Herbivorous Habitat - Jungle Favorite food - Bananas, leaves. TEMPER I am very playful and energetic! I can play, run and jump all day long! Come on, catch up with me… What, don't you want? Also tell me that you don't climb trees! Snow leopard Height: 166 cm Three sizes: B97 / W58 / H93 Birthday April 29 Predator Habitat - Taiga Favorite food - Meat, fish. TEMPER I am a thoughtful, prudent girl, and very patient. There is no hurry in the snowy taiga. Your booty from you will not go anywhere, Arr! What did you think? Here you either have an icy heart or you are prey! FEATURES Puzzle game Beautiful artwork Animated characters Relaxing music CG Gallery Mode Rotate mosaics to make a picture.
